cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite both this package and the parent MDStatR engine it is derived from."
title: rolescry
type: software
version: 0.1.0
license: Apache-2.0
abstract: "Deterministic, name-blind variable-role detection for tabular datasets via information-theoretic signatures (Shannon entropy, normalized mutual information). Extracted from the MDStatR biostatistics engine. No LLMs, no external data transmission."
